
"Markdown" = "**Scene 1** (3 sec)\n***-Voiceover***: \"Hey Instagram fam! We\'re here today with an amazing offer just for you!\"\n***-Visual***: A lively shot of the host with a smile, winking at the camera, showing a vibrant background.\n\n**Scene 2** (4 sec)\n***-Voiceover***: \"For the first time and exclusively on Instagram, we\'re offering a very special discount on our service.\"\n***-Visual***: The host pulls out a large sign from behind, revealing the words \"EXCLUSIVE DISCOUNT\".\n\n**Scene 3** (3 sec)\n***-Voiceover***: \"We\'re talking about \'The only way\'. Trust us, it\'s unique and something you don\'t want to miss.\"\n***-Visual***: A brief, fancy shot of \"The only way\" product or logo, with sparkling effects.\n\n**Scene 4** (3 sec)\n***-Voiceover***: \"With \'The only way\', we promise to enhance your experience like never before. It\'s a game-changer.\"\n***-Visual***: Close-up of the host with a confident look, holding the product or pointing towards the logo.\n\n**Scene 5** (3 sec)\n***-Voiceover***: \"Ready for the biggest reveal? We\'re offering an unbeatable discount on \'The only way\'.\"\n***-Visual***: The screen dissolves into a big, bold graphic showing the discount rate in large numbers.\n\n**Scene 6** (4 sec)\n***-Voiceover***: \"Yes, you heard it right. This discount is available for a limited time, so grab it before it\'s gone.\"\n***-Visual***: Host is holding a giant clock pointing at the time running out. A sense of urgency is created.\n\n**Scene 7** (3 sec)\n***-Voiceover***: \"Join us, enjoy \'The only way\', and let\'s make the most of this exclusive offer together!\"\n***-Visual***: The host gives a thumbs-up to the camera, then the screen transitions to a \'Swipe Up\' to take action sort of animation.";
